I choose a oil noodle with 2 dishes,  white radish & fried bean balls., it cost $44.00 price is not cheap in this area. I ask the man for how to order and he is not polite to answer. Overall comment food is fair and not good service ., must have more other choose in this area.
Delicious cart noodle shop. Change of owner but soup and food quality were still maintained as the old owner are still working there. Highly recommend.
Clean Restaurant with warm family environment. Soup is my favourite and they are expert in soup. Nice place for family.

result.adr_address: 32-40號 Wellington St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Yung Kee Restaurant

reviews.text: If you have only one shot at trying out the roast goose in Hong Kong, this is the place to go. They have been in operations for more than half a century. The roast goose is here is tender and juicy. The other dishes are remarkable as well. I came back the next day to purchase some Chinese sausages for mom. Alas, it was a business dinner and I couldn't take out my phone to snap each dish!
Good roast goose meat and good service staff. The soup is superb! A little pricey place.

This is still a great restaurant after so many years. This is according to my Wife and friends who have been here on numerous occasions. I have been to Hong Kong over the last 20 years but never visited.

I told myself to booked in advance for my next trip to Hong Kong. I must say that I was not disappointed despite its size which was smaller than I have expected. This is because I have had goose in Taiwan and Malaysia that were huge in comparison.

The premium pork belly was good but would have been better if it did not taste so porky. Overall a great experience and I would recommend it.

It’s about 6 mins walk from central station.

A roast meat restaurant and a place to die for! Great ambience , service and food. Obviously the roast goose and char siu are really out of this world. Standards have been maintained over the years. Will continue to pursue the good life of dining experience here
Amazing food, service with a smile!! We were very happy with our meal. The waiter recommended the double boiled abalone soup which was super awesome!!

result.adr_address: 8 Mau Yip Rd, Metro City, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 8 Mau Yip Rd, Metro City, Hong Kong
result.name: MCP Discovery

reviews.text:
Good to just walk around. There are different choices for eating from Chinese to Western food. Also, there are different types of shops for you to shop around such as clothing and appliances. Children are also welcome in there for playing games in play room, as well as examining models and toys.
On the other hand, there are clinics to heal people and animals. Also large and small supermarkets for daily usage. Travel agents for you to plan your short and long trips. Banks and ATM machines are available for you to draw money for spending.
When you are tired, there are messages chairs for you to consider.
From time to time, there is a main event or show to attract people.
Should look at it as one whole integrated Mall instead of three separate malls since you can get through easily. Just go there and explore more.
Ok for locals or a quick visit to eat but standard shops everywhere in hk so no shopping for me.
A great variety of shops.
Lots of varieties, large selections of shops and eateries.
Not many things to buy

result.adr_address: 香港新都城貿業路8號
result.name: 新都城中心三期商場

reviews.text: 以前每日放學成日行👍

有改善空間，可重新規劃惠康及傢俬店間格，拆走中庭的手扶電梯，釋放中庭空間舉辦多些大型活動，吸引人流逗留。
定期要求商户裝修店舖，增强新鲜感。
擴大洗手間厠格空間，並加強清潔，給遊人舒適環境。

Metro II, 就peoples mountain, peoples sea.

然而，Metropolis，比較清幽，清雅。

大朝早，有白衫袍一清抹牆身，地下，有repairmen doing repairs and maintenance works.

有家庭...熱廚房用品铺；有孩兒進修學習地铺；

有大型超市，這超市通常在10: 15 p.m. 上架新鲜菜菓，菜菓清涼有光澤...

有專硏買一送一新鮮出爐蛋tart, 波羅包...

只是數筆，待老街坊，老友記..延寫下去...

Thanks.

Eric Wong.

result.adr_address: 香港九龍城打鼓嶺道80號
result.formatted_address: 香港九龍城打鼓嶺道80號
result.name: 榕記車仔麵

reviews.text:
車仔麵而有胡椒豬肚湯底，確實別處所無，且相當合拍，豬肚炆得剛好，軟化得來不失有咬口，比一般酒樓的不是太硬就是太輭更好，且味精不重，豬腸也有同様效果，所以如叫這湯底，可以叫別様餸，因兩款味太似，早知試牛腩！沙嗲尤魚醬味偏甜，和胡椒的辢味又似乎很配，不錯，由其是老闆特意用小碗上和主湯分開，刻意的安排讓食者能品嘗到甜沙嗲的效果，可見是用心的厨藝！
豆腐柏葉口感非常好，如食日本蛋角豆腐但豆香甚濃，必食之選！
未試過食車仔麵連湯都飲埋，老闆有heart,環境有情調，情侶拍拖一流，推介!
垃圾，份量少，夜晚去奶茶檸茶都冇
只是扮高級的車仔麵，其實食物相當普通，唔值比較贵的價格!
上次食雞絲已經好似橡筋咁，蘿蔔又難食，今次落單時已講左豬手要另上，結果都係放埋一齊😅，失望到呢～
